{"id":540410,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/09/声称谷歌屏蔽希拉里负面信息的是英媒吗？/","date":"2016-09-13T23:32:07Z","modified":"2016-09-14T05:44:03Z","title":"【弄个大新闻】声称“谷歌屏蔽希拉里负面信息”的不是英媒是俄媒","content":"<p>《中国日报网》近日发表了一篇题为《英媒：谷歌屏蔽希拉里负面信息 或影响300万选票归属》的文章，并得到环球网、东方网、腾讯网、搜狐网等各大网站转载。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/chinadaily_hillary.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-540411\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/chinadaily_hillary.jpg\" alt=\"chinadaily_hillary\" width=\"500\" height=\"164\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/chinadaily_hillary.jpg 1350w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/chinadaily_hillary-300x99.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/chinadaily_hillary-768x253.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/chinadaily_hillary-1024x337.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://world.chinadaily.com.cn/2016-09/13/content_26786888.htm\" target=\"_blank\">中国日报｜英媒：谷歌屏蔽希拉里负面信息 或影响300万选票归属</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>据英国《每日邮报》9月12日报道，一位研究型心理学家近日调查证实，谷歌确实进行暗箱操作来帮助希拉里。</p>\n<p>美国行为研究和技术研究所（American Institute for Behavioral Research and Technology）心理学家罗伯特·爱泼斯坦在俄罗斯卫星通讯社刊文指出，谷歌公司过滤甚至屏蔽掉对希拉里不利的信息，这种行为很可能会影响到11月总统大选中300万张选票的归属。</p></blockquote>\n<p>俄罗斯卫星通讯社（Sputnik）是刊登<a href=\"https://sputniknews.com/us/20160912/1045214398/google-clinton-manipulation-election.html\" target=\"_blank\">原始报道</a>的网站，英国小报《每日邮报》只是在通篇<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3785801/Is-Google-manipulating-autocomplete-results-favor-Clinton.html\" target=\"_blank\">转述</a>卫星通讯社的文章内容。耐人寻味的是，<strong>中国日报网在标题中强调了“英媒”，而非刊出原始报道的卫星通讯社。</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_540412\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/dailymail_sputnik.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-540412\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/dailymail_sputnik.png\" alt=\"dailymail_sputnik\" width=\"450\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/dailymail_sputnik.png 1314w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/dailymail_sputnik-300x236.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/dailymail_sputnik-768x603.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/dailymail_sputnik-1024x804.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">英国《每日邮报》通篇转述了俄罗斯卫星通讯社的报道；网页截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_540413\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/sputnik_hillary.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-540413\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/sputnik_hillary.jpg\" alt=\"sputnik_hillary\" width=\"500\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/sputnik_hillary.jpg 1579w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/sputnik_hillary-300x178.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/sputnik_hillary-768x456.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/sputnik_hillary-1024x608.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/sputnik_hillary-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">俄罗斯卫星通讯社原文页面截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/04/%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%83%B5%E5%B0%B8%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%82%B9%E8%B5%9E%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%BA%A7%E8%B0%88%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2/\" target=\"_blank\">【立此存照】僵尸账号也能“点赞”习近平座谈会讲话</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/07/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%8D%8E%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E5%9C%A8%E8%AF%B4%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E4%BF%84%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF/\" target=\"_blank\">【立此存照】新华国际到底在说哪个“今日俄罗斯”？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/01/%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e4%ba%9a%e5%b7%9e%ef%bd%9c%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%e8%ae%b0%e8%80%85%e5%af%b9%e3%80%8a%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e6%97%a5%e6%8a%a5%e3%80%8b%e6%96%ad%e7%ab%a0%e5%8f%96%e4%b9%89%e5%85%b6%e8%a7%82/\" target=\"_blank\">自由亚州｜美国记者对《中国日报》断章取义其观点表示不满</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>附：维基百科对<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sputnik_(news_agency)\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯卫星通讯社</a>的简介</strong>（鉴于维基百科词条是由用户编辑，中国数字时代保留了该词条内容的原始信息来源，以便读者查询确认）</p>\n<blockquote><p><b>Sputnik</b>(pronounced spʊtnɪk) is an online news and radio broadcast service established by the Russian government-controlled news agency Rossiya Segodnya.<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sputnik_%28news_agency%29#cite_note-Al_Jazeera_America-2\">[2]</a> Headquartered in Moscow, Sputnik has regional editorial offices in Washington, Cairo, Beijing and London. It focuses on global politics and economics and is geared entirely towards a non-Russian audience.<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sputnik_%28news_agency%29#cite_note-3\">[3]</a> Sputnik has been subject to accusations of bias, disinformation<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sputnik_%28news_agency%29#cite_note-MacFarquhar-4\">[4]</a> and being a Russian propaganda outlet.<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sputnik_%28news_agency%29#cite_note-foreignpolicy.com-5\">[5]</a><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sputnik_%28news_agency%29#cite_note-Sputnik._Propaganda_in_a_New_Orbit-6\">[6]</a></p>\n<p>（编者译）卫星通讯社是一个提供新闻和广播服务的网站，由俄罗斯政府控制的“今日俄罗斯通讯社”（Rossiya Segodnya）设立。卫星通讯社总部位于莫斯科，在华盛顿特区、开罗、北京和伦敦设有分站。其内容侧重于全球政治和经济，全部内容均为非俄罗斯读者打造。卫星通讯社被指有偏见、造谣的问题，是俄罗斯外宣的一部分。</p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[15085,23589,8616,19607]}